headline: Leerink starts coverage on Boston Scientific and Medtronic with bullish ratings
summary: Investing.com -- Leerink Partners began coverage on three of the largest medical technology companies on Monday, assigning bullish ratings to Boston Scientific (NYSE:BSX) and Medtronic (NYSE:MDT), while taking a more neutral stance on Abbott Laboratories (NYSE:ABT)
